        "id": 1000825
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-08-16T22:26:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The purpose of DCHECK(flushed) is to prevent caller from calling Write() but not Flush(), I actually should have bool alert_flush_not_called \u003d false, turn it on in Write() and turn it off in Flush, and dcheck it destructor.\n\nIt seems not related to initialization, right?",
      "parentUuid": "ee6860ad_20466b88",
      "revId": "7438e06f309a431d675c1b81e75fc31071f20d2b",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
